he rules","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of your campaign. Keys beginning with ","type":"text"},{"code":"$","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" are reserved for Superwall and will be dropped. Values can be any","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"JSON encodable value, URLs or Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be dropped.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"paywallOverrides","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides"},{"type":"text","text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" and the SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall."}]}],"name":"onRequestDismiss"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A completion block that accepts an ","type":"text"},{"code":"Error","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and returns a ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". This will show when the requested","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"paywall is skipped. Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"EmptyView()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"name":"onErrorView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard"},{"text":". If the paywall is set to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Non Gated"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", this will be called when","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gated"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"feature"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This uses "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Superwall\/getPaywall(forPlacement:params:paywallOverrides:delegate:)"},{"type":"text","text":" under the hood."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Warning","style":"warning","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re responsible for the deallocation of this view. If you have a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" presented somewhere"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and you try to present the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" elsewhere, you will get a crash."}]}]}]}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/superwallkit\/paywallview\/init(placement:params:paywalloverrides:onrequestdismiss:onerrorview:feature:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"